(1, 'The SM15V 2-way floor monitor sports a mighty 15&quot; speaker perfectly paired with a 2&quot; horn.', 'The Yamaha SM15V Club Series V Monitor is sturdy, solid, and compact. Gigging bands, mobile DJs, and houses of worship helped make the first 4 generations of Yamaha Club Series Speakers incredibly popular. The refinements of generation V continue this success story with larger enclosures for improved low-frequency performance, improved drivers for higher power handling, redesigned crossovers, stronger grilles, and dual Speakon and 1/4&quot; connectors.', NULL, NULL, 'Yamaha SM15V', 0x613a303a7b7d, NULL, 0x613a313a7b693a303b613a333a7b733a383a226368696c645f6964223b733a323a223133223b733a363a22656e74697479223b733a353a226d65646961223b733a363a2264626e616d65223b733a343a22636f7265223b7d7d, NULL, NULL),
(2, 'The compact, trapezoidal-shaped EV T252 is an 800-watt two way high efficiency constant-directivity stage system.', 'The T252+ comes with two state- of-the-art DL15ST 15-inch woofers with excellent low- frequency output, very low distortion and unequalled long- term fatigue resistance. Rotatable horn ensures minimal coverage overlap and gives excellent performance in arrays. Ideal for systems where a subwoofer cannot be used. 800 watts continuous, 3200 watts peak power handling. Ideal for systems where a subwoofer cannot be used. Rotatable horn ensures minimal coverage overlap and gives excellent performance in arrays. Roadworthy enclosure with metal corners and grille, and heavy-duty handles Contant-directivity 60x40 horn Biampable, passive network included', NULL, NULL, 'Electro-Voice T252', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(3, 'The Max 15 is engineered to provide a high output and still maintain a maximum fidelity. The Max 15 loudspeaker incorporates a 15â€ low frequency woofer and a 2.06â€ voice coil high frequency compression driver. The Max 15 is able to handle 300 watts of amplifier power and a peak power of 600 watts.', 'The Max 15 is engineered to provide a high output and still maintain a maximum fidelity. The Max 15 loudspeaker incorporates a 15â€ low frequency woofer and a 2.06â€ voice coil high frequency compression driver. The woofer is mounted in a vented enclosure that is tuned for optimum low frequency response. The compression driver is mounted on a constant directivity horn.  The Max 15 has a multiple of hanging points allowing the enclosure to be mounted vertical and horizontal. The Max 15 is equipped with 13 treaded point for eye bolt placement. The enclosure is asymmetric in shape allowing it to be used as a floor monitor and is finished in a Black textured paint finish. The speaker uses a NL4 type connector.  The system produces a frequency response from 50Hz to 18KHz and is capable of producing a peak level of 125dB. The components inside the Max 15 are able to handle 300 watts of amplifier power and a peak power of 600 watts.', NULL, NULL, 'Biema Max 15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(4, 'Ultra compact LED wash. The Q70 has 7 10-watt quad die LEDs. Beam angle is 25 degrees.', 'The Baby Color Q70 from Mega-Lite is a bright color changing fixture that&Atilde;&cent;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12;&iuml;&iquest;&frac12;s ultra compact in size. Equipped with 7 10-watt LEDs and less than a 5\\\\\\&quot; square body, the output of the Baby Color Q70 contends with the output of larger fixtures. The RGBW quad-chip LEDs produce a wide range of colors, including pastel shades. And, they also makes the face of the LEDs appears uniform in color. The fixture has a 25&Atilde;ï¿½&Acirc;&deg; beam angle and comes with a diffuser that increases the beam angle to 50&Atilde;ï¿½&Acirc;&deg;. The Baby Color Q70 is controllable via DMX 512 and has strobe, macro and dimmer effects. It also has control options audio trigger and master slave. The Baby Color Q70 has a double mounting yoke so it can to be set upon the floor or hang from a structure. It has a digital display designed for ease of use. And, it is equipped with power con in and out and 3-pin XLR connection inputs and outputs.', NULL, NULL, 'Mega Baby Color Q70', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5, 'The N-E Color Punch delivers saturated colors that will knock you out! This ultra compact unit is a perfect for truss warming, uplighting and small stages', 'The N-E Color Punch delivers saturated colors that will knock you out! This ultra compact unit is a perfect for truss warming and measures 10.25\\\"L x 3.5\\\"W x 9.25\\\"H. Made with 12 3-watt tri chip RGB LEDs, it produces smooth, vibrant color mixing. The beam angle is 25Â°.  Daisy chain installation is possible with the Neutrix power con in & out. This unit is controlled via DMX, with 3 modes of operation.', NULL, NULL, 'Mega NE-Color Punch', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(6, 'XL Beam 300 is a 300W moving head with optics that provide 22,000 lumens of output. CMY mixing and 6 degree beam.', 'XL Beam 300 is a 300W moving head with an exceptional number of features. It uses the Phillips Fast Fit MSR Gold lamp, with superior optics that provide 22,000 lumens of output. There are seven rotating gobos that are easily interchangeable. What makes this fixture so robust though, are the range of additional features. It offers three beam angle options - 6 degree zoom, 9 degree frost and 20 degree heavy frost. There is a linearly adjustable focus, dimmer and iris. And, it is a CYM colour mixing fixture with 7 dichroic colour filters. The XL Beam is a unit that is equipped to impress.', NULL, NULL, 'PR XL 300 Beam', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(7, '400 watt black light cannon. Simple plug and play operation.', 'This high intensity black light cannon is ideal for those serious about black light. It uses a HPS lamp so you get true back light UV rays.', NULL, NULL, 'Black Light Cannon - 400 watt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(8, 'The MG102c has a total of 10 input channels. Two of the stereo channels can be used as mono microphone inputs, providing a total of four microphone inputs when necessary. Gain trim covers a wide -60dB to -16dB range for microphone input, and -34dB to +10dB for line input.', 'The MG102C is an ideal mixer for basic music production or live sound applications that require high sound quality from a relatively small number of input sources. While remarkably compact and lightweight, no compromises have been made in sound quality. It even has built-in channel compressors that, although easy to operate, can significantly enhance the quality of your mixes. An optional adaptor allows mounting on a microphone stand for easy access and convenient positioning on stage.', NULL, NULL, 'Yamaha MG102c', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
