(20, 'Audio Technica ST90MKII Dynamic Handheld Vocal Microphone The Audio Technica ST90MKII is a high quality dynamic microphone that&#39;s tough enough to be used in any professional situation.', 'Audio Technica ST90MKII Dynamic Handheld Vocal Microphone The Audio Technica ST90MKII is a high quality dynamic microphone that&#39;s tough enough to be used in any professional situation. Ideal for the stage or studio where crisp, clear vocals are a must! This is the perfect mic for vocalists or performers. Designed to be one tough cookie this microphone can withstand all the rigors of a full scale tour or the simplicity of any home recording studio. The ST90mkII features an on-off switch, plus requires no phantom power you can use it with just about any mixer, PA or self-powered speaker. The Audio Technica ST90MKII also has a high degree of feedback rejection, and can tolerate exceptionally loud sound sources, making this feature packed microphone ideal in any live situation, in front of guitar amps or on top of snare drums. Product Features: Tough, Rugged construction Built-in on/off switch Shockproof grille Dynamic Cardioid pattern Low impedence Includes handy stand mount.', NULL, NULL, 'Audio Technica ST90 Microphone', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
