(92, 'Front/Rear Fast Fold projection screen. 16:9 aspect ratio.', 'This versatile screen is easy to set up in minutes and is great for presentations, movie nights or anywhere a dynamic screen is needed. A dual projection surface allows you to front or rear project allowing this screen to fit nearly any application.', NULL, NULL, '5.5ft x 10ft Projection Screen', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
